<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/22477436">武侠世界里的人靠什么吃饭？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="1171801" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">总感觉武侠世界里的大侠光顾着打打杀杀了，他们从哪来的钱吃饭呢？</div>


</div>
