</a>



<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="672">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$huang-jin-28" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/huang-jin-28" class="zg-link" title="黄今">黄今</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="1171801" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">看的武侠片不多，比较喜欢李连杰演的，就以Jet Lee系列为例，来说说这个问题吧。<br><br><br>1. 自给自足型<br><br>《少林寺》里的大师兄说：<br>“方丈，饥民每日不断，长此下去，少林虽有庙产，也难免坐吃山空啊。”<br><br><noscript><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/24820028189f929b060a03110d719f1b_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="850" data-rawheight="362" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="850" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/24820028189f929b060a03110d719f1b_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="850" data-rawheight="362" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="850" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/24820028189f929b060a03110d719f1b_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic4.zhimg.com/24820028189f929b060a03110d719f1b_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/96535e1a081eb4b9a1d997a9601a2b61_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="853" data-rawheight="359" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="853" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/96535e1a081eb4b9a1d997a9601a2b61_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="853" data-rawheight="359" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="853" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/96535e1a081eb4b9a1d997a9601a2b61_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic2.zhimg.com/96535e1a081eb4b9a1d997a9601a2b61_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/3a559159ffef3ff3664348012ec60151_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="848" data-rawheight="361" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="848" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/3a559159ffef3ff3664348012ec60151_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="848" data-rawheight="361" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="848" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/3a559159ffef3ff3664348012ec60151_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic2.zhimg.com/3a559159ffef3ff3664348012ec60151_b.jpg"><br><br>由“少林虽有庙产”可见，少林寺并不只靠香客上山和弟子化缘，他们自己有一定资本积累，平时还能接济接济穷苦大众。不过本片的背景是“隋朝末年，天下大乱”，所以寺里的财政也跟着紧张起来了。<br><br>“山门只有清茶淡饭， 怕救不活他（李连杰）。”<br><noscript><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/696f79e810c9b64562d53d4661ee3265_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="848" data-rawheight="357" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="848" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/696f79e810c9b64562d53d4661ee3265_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="848" data-rawheight="357" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="848" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/696f79e810c9b64562d53d4661ee3265_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic2.zhimg.com/696f79e810c9b64562d53d4661ee3265_b.jpg"><br><br>以至于少林弟子要到野地里去摸蛤蟆救治李连杰。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/4e726b9d341e0afcf5b3509cd0227dc2_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="848" data-rawheight="360" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="848" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/4e726b9d341e0afcf5b3509cd0227dc2_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="848" data-rawheight="360" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="848" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/4e726b9d341e0afcf5b3509cd0227dc2_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic3.zhimg.com/4e726b9d341e0afcf5b3509cd0227dc2_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/5a4888aa609776b2443f2d9200c041b8_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="849" data-rawheight="363" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="849" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/5a4888aa609776b2443f2d9200c041b8_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="849" data-rawheight="363" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="849" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/5a4888aa609776b2443f2d9200c041b8_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic1.zhimg.com/5a4888aa609776b2443f2d9200c041b8_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/c70b72b0a0ef43dc7d6662ffdedf0bc1_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="851" data-rawheight="364" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="851" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/c70b72b0a0ef43dc7d6662ffdedf0bc1_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="851" data-rawheight="364" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="851" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/c70b72b0a0ef43dc7d6662ffdedf0bc1_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic2.zhimg.com/c70b72b0a0ef43dc7d6662ffdedf0bc1_b.jpg"><br><br><br>2. 个体经营型<br><br>黄飞鸿是开药店的（和西门庆一样），就是宝芝林。并且不光卖药，还管看病练武，可谓一个大型综合医疗保健服务机构，简称大保健。<br><br><noscript><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/e220b9c7e40e4c853a6fdba57670a129_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="748" data-rawheight="469" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="748" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/e220b9c7e40e4c853a6fdba57670a129_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="748" data-rawheight="469" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="748" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/e220b9c7e40e4c853a6fdba57670a129_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic2.zhimg.com/e220b9c7e40e4c853a6fdba57670a129_b.jpg"><br><br>另一方面，黄师傅还积极发展副业，这个舞龙舞狮、节日婚庆业务也是业界领先。<br>（这一部是赵文卓演的）<br><noscript><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/2cee503142682b6b0bc4320365226f82_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="840" data-rawheight="351" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="840" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/2cee503142682b6b0bc4320365226f82_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="840" data-rawheight="351" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="840" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/2cee503142682b6b0bc4320365226f82_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic3.zhimg.com/2cee503142682b6b0bc4320365226f82_b.jpg"><br><br>所以，虽然处在一个大青果药丸的时期，黄飞鸿的生活还是比较滋润的，没事儿戴个大墨镜，那么吃饭自然不成问题。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/89c6bd6a906854e06f1bd096ca0c4041_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="852" data-rawheight="360" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="852" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/89c6bd6a906854e06f1bd096ca0c4041_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="852" data-rawheight="360" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="852" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/89c6bd6a906854e06f1bd096ca0c4041_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic2.zhimg.com/89c6bd6a906854e06f1bd096ca0c4041_b.jpg"><br><br>3. 官富二代型<br><br>以方世玉为代表，家里做纺织品生意，他妈妈专门忽悠老外（实际差点被忽悠了）。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/5e6bbd14b4ec578f847b8c199e43a6a8_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="846" data-rawheight="475" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="846" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/5e6bbd14b4ec578f847b8c199e43a6a8_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="846" data-rawheight="475" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="846" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/5e6bbd14b4ec578f847b8c199e43a6a8_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic1.zhimg.com/5e6bbd14b4ec578f847b8c199e43a6a8_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/2a29345c5cb486243600fd0eb4885b5c_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="847" data-rawheight="465" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="847" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/2a29345c5cb486243600fd0eb4885b5c_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="847" data-rawheight="465" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="847" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/2a29345c5cb486243600fd0eb4885b5c_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic1.zhimg.com/2a29345c5cb486243600fd0eb4885b5c_b.jpg"><br><br>方世玉他爹跟各种达官显贵谈笑风生，显然是不用担心吃饭问题的。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/f9521dacd70af8ada3dcf45a07c87792_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="845" data-rawheight="474" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="845" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/f9521dacd70af8ada3dcf45a07c87792_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="845" data-rawheight="474" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="845" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/f9521dacd70af8ada3dcf45a07c87792_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic3.zhimg.com/f9521dacd70af8ada3dcf45a07c87792_b.jpg"><br><br>方世玉对服务业的行情非常了解，连拉皮条的都认识。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/c3fadf169f7e918fe85334faa2687b16_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="849" data-rawheight="478" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="849" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/c3fadf169f7e918fe85334faa2687b16_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="849" data-rawheight="478" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="849" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/c3fadf169f7e918fe85334faa2687b16_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic3.zhimg.com/c3fadf169f7e918fe85334faa2687b16_b.jpg"><br><br>前面说了黄飞鸿，就会想到苏乞儿。<br>苏察哈尔灿，他爹是广州军区司令。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/6c0825db79abc4bcbaad8a98fa2bdc3d_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="850" data-rawheight="465" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="850" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/6c0825db79abc4bcbaad8a98fa2bdc3d_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="850" data-rawheight="465" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="850" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/6c0825db79abc4bcbaad8a98fa2bdc3d_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic2.zhimg.com/6c0825db79abc4bcbaad8a98fa2bdc3d_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/ee95ef4421a822e032ae4e13850bcad9_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="843" data-rawheight="468" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="843" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/ee95ef4421a822e032ae4e13850bcad9_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="843" data-rawheight="468" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="843" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/ee95ef4421a822e032ae4e13850bcad9_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic2.zhimg.com/ee95ef4421a822e032ae4e13850bcad9_b.jpg"><br><br>难怪石榴姐笑的这么开心。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/87adb91493114d3896b5d42247c11f22_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="848" data-rawheight="470" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="848" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/87adb91493114d3896b5d42247c11f22_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="848" data-rawheight="470" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="848" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/87adb91493114d3896b5d42247c11f22_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic3.zhimg.com/87adb91493114d3896b5d42247c11f22_b.jpg"><br><br>4. 吃不上饭型<br><br>洪熙官本来是反政府武装成员，后来遭到出卖，只能带着儿子流落江湖，连吃碗面的钱都没有。<br><br><noscript><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/1cca6e0387bebe440b84383bd7f42ac9_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="844" data-rawheight="463" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="844" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/1cca6e0387bebe440b84383bd7f42ac9_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="844" data-rawheight="463" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="844" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/1cca6e0387bebe440b84383bd7f42ac9_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic2.zhimg.com/1cca6e0387bebe440b84383bd7f42ac9_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/e19e6685b2718da1a5a9bb54c7ef1cd0_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="846" data-rawheight="466" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="846" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/e19e6685b2718da1a5a9bb54c7ef1cd0_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="846" data-rawheight="466" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="846" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/e19e6685b2718da1a5a9bb54c7ef1cd0_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic1.zhimg.com/e19e6685b2718da1a5a9bb54c7ef1cd0_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/2a28d0b6eaf3564e7bdaf09d67a23d3a_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="846" data-rawheight="468" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="846" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/2a28d0b6eaf3564e7bdaf09d67a23d3a_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="846" data-rawheight="468" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="846" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/2a28d0b6eaf3564e7bdaf09d67a23d3a_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic3.zhimg.com/2a28d0b6eaf3564e7bdaf09d67a23d3a_b.jpg"><br><br>“忍无可忍，无需再忍”话音刚落两人的肚子都响了。<br><br>后来不得已只能拿给地主阶级充当打手，这才有口饭吃。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/87ffa5082ed75805d1931943caf2c2c9_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="836" data-rawheight="465" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="836" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/87ffa5082ed75805d1931943caf2c2c9_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="836" data-rawheight="465" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="836" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/87ffa5082ed75805d1931943caf2c2c9_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic2.zhimg.com/87ffa5082ed75805d1931943caf2c2c9_b.jpg"><br><br>但是饭已经被邱淑贞吃完了。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/e2878fcb0c02634653ed41d407367f2d_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="841" data-rawheight="465" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="841" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/e2878fcb0c02634653ed41d407367f2d_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="841" data-rawheight="465" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="841" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/e2878fcb0c02634653ed41d407367f2d_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic2.zhimg.com/e2878fcb0c02634653ed41d407367f2d_b.jpg"><br><br>5. 灰色收入型<br><br>一般主人公所在团队都不搞这个产业。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/d82b13d2d2971f9417415f2bb4f52119_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="846" data-rawheight="459" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="846" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/d82b13d2d2971f9417415f2bb4f52119_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="846" data-rawheight="459" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="846" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/d82b13d2d2971f9417415f2bb4f52119_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic2.zhimg.com/d82b13d2d2971f9417415f2bb4f52119_b.jpg"><br><br>因为过的是打打杀杀的生活，所以武林人士中多有杏林高手。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/d1c636163613d91d93a1fde59f1331eb_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="846" data-rawheight="460" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="846" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/d1c636163613d91d93a1fde59f1331eb_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="846" data-rawheight="460" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="846" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/d1c636163613d91d93a1fde59f1331eb_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic4.zhimg.com/d1c636163613d91d93a1fde59f1331eb_b.jpg"><br><br>6. 特供食品型<br><br>这个不用解释了吧。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/8fe4421c32c8ba1d35a93bb9407b58a3_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="846" data-rawheight="439" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="846" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/8fe4421c32c8ba1d35a93bb9407b58a3_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="846" data-rawheight="439" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="846" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/8fe4421c32c8ba1d35a93bb9407b58a3_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic4.zhimg.com/8fe4421c32c8ba1d35a93bb9407b58a3_b.jpg"><br><br>7.不知道吃什么型<br><br>秦始皇都不知道,。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/809b43175370d427f8003eb760f0e83e_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="847" data-rawheight="373" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="847" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/809b43175370d427f8003eb760f0e83e_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="847" data-rawheight="373" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="847" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/809b43175370d427f8003eb760f0e83e_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic3.zhimg.com/809b43175370d427f8003eb760f0e83e_b.jpg"><br><br>8. 自给自足型<br><br>毅种循环。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/f66f9672c775300e28f7903581c0ea26_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="512" data-rawheight="384" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="512" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/f66f9672c775300e28f7903581c0ea26_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="512" data-rawheight="384" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="512" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/f66f9672c775300e28f7903581c0ea26_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic3.zhimg.com/f66f9672c775300e28f7903581c0ea26_b.jpg">


